source.name: NYC Budget Revenue
source.description: Data set contains revenue for actual fiscal years and five financial plan fiscal years. Revenue include Taxes, Miscellaneous Revenues, Unrestricted Intergovernmental Aid, Disallowance of Categorical Grants, Federal Grants, State Grants, Other Categorical Grants, and Capital IFA.
